{"tid":1416322,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[8.5] 一人一句多謝前線手足","createTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:43:01.000Z","uid":266385,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ac0c447162bb7f4f5db049d7ecd3708f56f7d4","tid":1416322,"uid":266385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T14:53:20.000Z","msg":"P牌仔第一次開po因為真心好想多謝前線<br />\n事緣今日晏晝同朋友喺添馬參加緊有。不。反。對。通。知。書嘅集會<br />\n之後班狗又發癲起勢咁放TG<br />\n我同朋友今日都冇gear得個普通口罩<br />\n放咗咁多個彈，<br />\n集會近夏愨道嗰邊理應都會聞到<br />\n但今日冇，連煙都唔係好見到<br />\n後面上FB睇先知原來因為前線煙霧隊嘅手足勁到每個彈都好快整熄<br />\n你哋好犀利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家發夢夢見啲咩想多謝前線手足都歡迎講低<br />\n自問唔夠勇武，惟對前線無盡感激<br />\n<br />\n最後，各位發夢時記得<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">Be Humble  Be Polite</span></span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d168e8cacb9246142a561fea03916fa6aa5ca10","tid":1416322,"uid":266385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:26:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />自推"},{"pid":"a4db29afa793b02b1947548afd45550221c0be66","tid":1416322,"uid":266385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:30:13.000Z","msg":"再推"},{"pid":"1da8bb1d9f3fa973e3351a411fcddac6e7bec60c","tid":1416322,"uid":266385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T15:43:01.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}